items.title: #245: Allure of the Mean Friend
items.author: Chicago Public Media
items.subtitle: What is it about them, our mean friends? They treat us badly, they don't call us back, they cancel plans at the last minute, and yet we come back for more. Popular bullies exist in business, politics, everywhere. How do they stay so popular?
